Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:08.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the biggest, most in-depth video about bowling ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:08.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,How bowling balls are made,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,the best way to throw them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,maximize strikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,how the lanes are oiled,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,what it takes to be a pro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:17.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,and how this sport has continually been reinvented
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:17.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:22.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,for literally thousands of years, up to the present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:22.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the science of bowling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:29.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,the most popular participatory sport in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:29.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm super impressed with how that went.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm even more impressed than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What is inside a bowling ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:41.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,I sent this ball to Creative Electron to get a 3D x-ray scan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:41.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:44.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:44.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:44.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:48.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,I always expected bowling balls to be, y’know, perfect solid spheres,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:48.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:53.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,but there's something inside here and it's not symmetric
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:53.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it's not even centered in the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I went to Storm Bowling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,one of only 11 bowling ball manufacturers in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,to find out how bowling balls are made.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. Basically when we make bowling balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,we always start in the center
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the center part of the bowling ball is the weight block.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:13.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,And as you can see this is an example of an asymmetrical shaped weight block,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:13.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,so it's actually a different shape about the X, the Y and the Z axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:18.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:26.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The weight blocks are embedded in a core of lightweight glass beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:26.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That is so silky-soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:35.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have not felt anything this soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.60,0:01:35.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:40.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's the difference in density between this sort of filling material and this core?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:40.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:41.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:41.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,About two and a half to three times more dense
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:47.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,in the inner weight block than it is in the core material.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:47.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,- If you were to look for example at this actual core,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,number one, it says 960
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,which means that it weighs 9.60 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:01.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then the description here underneath, which is a 03,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:01.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,this indicates what type of a weight block is inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:04.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What happens over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So this area right here is our urethane area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,So basically what we have are a number of different tanks that are set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,So there's a chemical reaction that occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,once it actually fills the mold
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:20.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we pour that cover stock material around the pour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:20.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,It gets extremely hot in just a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,You go right down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:27.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:31.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,she's actually pouring the pin material inside the tops of those cores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:31.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you can see for this particular bowling ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:33.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's a bright orange type of a material,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,and she's actually filling that hole with that plug material.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've got the lane at the right here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:45.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,which is where we take the balls that come out of the mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:45.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:48.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then they actually spin almost 2000 RPM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:48.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,On top of there there's the blades that come around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it actually makes the balls perfectly round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,So they'll actually trim those up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Since the balls are not symmetric,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,they are heavier on one side than the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,- And you can see there the last four or five pumps of air,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,where it actually floats the air then it stops and pauses,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,that the ball has completely settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:06.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then basically a needle will come out from the bottom part
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden it'll shoot it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then it'll be where the center of gravity is on the surface of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:19.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- When it comes right off the lane, right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:19.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,it is extremely porous and very, very dull,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there is a ton of friction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:23.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,between the ball and the lane at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,So every ball from right here will be smoothed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's just a matter of how much it's gonna be smoothed up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,in order to get what is the desired finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] But before they can use these balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,they have to be drilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,But that is specific to each bowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,How many balls are you making a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Steve] We're making over 3000 balls in a day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,they come out of this plant right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:58.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:58.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I found the bowling ball equivalent of clickbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,"You won't believe your eyes",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:04.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,"The mind bending hook".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\an3}- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. It's how you have to sell your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\an3}- Exactly. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] But how did it come to be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, bowling seems to be an ancient game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:20.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Archeologists have found wall drawings of a sport
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:20.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:26.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,that looks like bowling in an ancient Egyptian tomb dating back 7,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:26.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,In Germany, bowling was used as a religious ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pins represented your sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,so you're a good Christian if you could knock them all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Martin Luther himself was apparently a bowling fanatic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,and fixed the number of pins at nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,When the game made its way over to America,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:45.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,nine-pin bowling was banned because it promoted gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:45.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,The legend goes that people cleverly came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:50.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,10-pin bowling to get around the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:50.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa, totally different game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:56.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Today in the US, nine-pin bowling is only played in Texas
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:56.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,because it was the one state that didn't ban it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,instead, charging it tax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:00.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bowling lanes are about three-and-a-half-feet wide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,and 60 feet long down to the headpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:11.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm using Imperial units here because that's actually how they're defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:11.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,The lane is made of 39 narrow boards
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,that bowlers number for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,They used to be made of maple and pinewood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,but these days, most lanes are synthetic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,and made of fine particles coated with melamine resin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,One game of bowling gives you 10 frames
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,with two throws per frame
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,to try to knock down all 10 pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:35.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,The highest score you can get in a game without a strike is only 190,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:35.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,but strikes allow you to double count your next two throws,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,so a perfect game with all strikes gives you a score of 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you're anything like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,the whole game is just trying to throw the ball as straight as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,down the middle of the lane, hit the headpin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,and try to take as many other pins down with it as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna give me any tips or-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I've watched LeBron bowling, you won't be worse than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You say that now you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,- See, that's what I would normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I would normally be like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,reasonably happy with a shot like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,But for pro-bowlers like Pete Weber or Chris Barnes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.08,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Narrator] For a perfect game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:11.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] The game is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,And not just because they are way better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:16.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Narrator] And he get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:16.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Who you think that you are? I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hitting the headpins square on is not the perfect strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:27.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you hit the headpin square on going straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,you're unlikely to knock down all the pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:37.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,You could end up with a split where the ball goes through the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:37.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:41.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,or with the ball deflecting off to one side after hitting the headpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:41.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Chances for a strike are much higher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:47.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,if the center of the ball hits the pins just to one side of the headpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:47.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Board 17 and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:53.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,In which case the ball takes out the 1, 3, 5, and 9 pins,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:53.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,which take out the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So we want the ball to hit the 1 pin, the 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,the pin behind the 1, which is the 5 pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then the 9 or the 8 and the 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] You want the ball to hit all of those pins?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Chris] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Now the pins don't always fall this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,but the pin shape helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Pins roll in circles like eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,which help knock down the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's right baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,You wanted it, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] But to have an over 90% chance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:24.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,of getting a strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,the center of the ball has to hit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,with an error smaller than half a board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Needless to say, throwing a ball 60 feet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:35.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,straight at a target smaller than a dime is a tough task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:35.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Especially to do it consistently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Luckily there is a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Now, if we look at the pins
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,and as you look at them from here, from straight on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,the spot between the headpin,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,the one that's in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the 3 pin which is just right at that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,that gap's pretty narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,But as the ball hooks more,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,now we basically shift over,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:59.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,and now that space is considerably wider.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:59.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] If you can hit the pins not head-on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,but at an angle of six degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,you dramatically increase your chances of knocking them all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now the margin for error is greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:10.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:15.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,The ball can be coming in anywhere from board 17 to 18 and a half,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:15.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,that is a board and a half of room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that still gives you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,greater than a 90% chance of a strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:21.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, six degrees may not sound like a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it's actually extremely difficult to hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,The problem is, if you wanted to throw the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,straight at the pins and hit them at six degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:35.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,you would have to be bowling from 3/4 over on the next lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:35.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, with the two gutters in between and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:40.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:44.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the solution is you've got to curve the ball on one lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:44.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have never spun a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that… (laughs) Is that hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So if you've got it under your hand and the ball's underneath,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you're trying to spin it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,that's especially the motion that players use these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:56.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] This really became a big part of the sport by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The wood gets beat up with the damage from all the balls going into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,And so they basically created slip agents,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:08.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,lubricants much like oil on a car
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:08.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,so that the lanes didn't get damaged so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] So the original idea was to protect the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The original idea was just to protect the surface of the lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was not to manufacture anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,for my competitive-scoring type environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But applying oil to protect the wood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:23.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,meant that balls no longer grip the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,and roll without slipping down to the pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Instead they could skid,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,rotating not in their direction of travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I've been to a lot of bowling alleys before making this video
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I noticed it was a bit greasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I always thought that was just the nature of bowling alleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like the stinky rental shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,I didn't know they intentionally put oil on the lanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Vox has a great video specifically about oil patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:57.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,These days, there are machines specifically for applying oil to the lanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:57.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Chris] And then as proprietors went,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:09:59.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,"Huh, well yeah, it does make the ball skid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, if I put more in the middle than the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,my baller's bowl a little bit better and they're happier."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then as technology advances like everything does
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,now we have $30,000 lane machines
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,that can put a specific amount of oil on each board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] They work kind of like dot matrix printers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:17.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,They can lay the oil on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,with varying degrees of thickness across the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,and extend the oil pattern different distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,There are hundreds of different patterns that can be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:30.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Usually the oil extends about 2/3 the way down the lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:30.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,so to around 40 or 45 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:36.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,But there's always a dry patch of wood before the pins
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:36.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,that increases the friction with the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,getting it to start rolling without slipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,And this leads to the three parts of any pro bowler's throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,The skid, {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}the hook and the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,The skid, the hook {\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}and the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,The skid, the hook and the roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,When a bowler releases the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,it can be going 20 miles an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,and spinning at 500 RPM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's nearly 10 full revolutions per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Right-handers typically throw the ball to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,on the lane while spinning it to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:05.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,During the skid phase, the ball slides down the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,spinning but not rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,As it comes to the end of the oil,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:15.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,the friction increases and the ball accelerates to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:15.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,It hooks because of its spin,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the spin starts lining up with the direction of travel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:23.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,leading to stage three, roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:23.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,The ball is rolling without slipping as it barrels into the pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ideally, as close to that six degree angle as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Like the ball starts on the left side of the lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,goes straight across almost rightmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:43.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then hooks like at the last minute, rolls in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:43.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,So that's almost like a perfect shot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,straight in the pocket there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\an3}- Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. That's where you want to hit the pins. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:50.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- My very first game,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,it was ABC back then, American Bowling Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I filled out the application to bowl in men's league.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dad gave them the letter saying that I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the first game of bowl was 300
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they handed me a hundred dollars too,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it was like, yeah, making money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:16.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,And actually, my first, my sixth, my ninth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:16.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:21.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,my 13th, 17th, 20th were all 300 games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:21.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:25.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I like, seven or eight 300 in my first year of men's league.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:25.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:30.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- To shoot 300 you have to get lucky somewhere along the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:30.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:37.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,It came in to hit the 1, 3, 5, 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:41.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that that's what we call the perfect shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I mean, you just keep hitting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's almost the identical shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at that, that yellow and the purple,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,they're almost exactly on top of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, it just goes a little bit straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.87,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That one, the purple one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,was just a little bit higher on the head pin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it still hit the 1, 3 and the 5 and the 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can't get much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:15.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] This type of throw is only possible because of the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:15.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you try to throw a ball the same way on an unoiled lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I actually ask you to bowl like you normally would,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,but on the dry lane?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know it's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just want to see what like a normal shot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\an1}would look like if there was no oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's gonna hit the lane and go in the left gutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's what I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:35.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:35.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna throw it just like it's a regular lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:38.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:38.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh yeah, there's no oil on the lane so the ball can't get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,As soon as it hits the lane, it's going to start hooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,y'know, 'cause if you do this, who's skidding a ball on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So they want the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. We need the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we didn't have oil, this is what it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,And nobody would have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is not fun. - The bowling sucks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,We don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- For pro bowlers, the oil on the lane is a key part of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wow. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Do you look at the oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to scope it out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:22.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,or are you just kind of guessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:22.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:26.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I usually don't look at the oil. I let my ball be the guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:26.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Y‘know, I know some guys that are… they get down like this
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:30.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:33.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they look in and it's like…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:33.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,they're seeing the same thing I do when I sit down, I go like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I see absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Whether you can see it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,figuring out the condition of oil on the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,can make the difference between a strike and a miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,As the game wears on the bowling balls move the oil around,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,pushing it further down the lane and stripping it off the most common paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,So players have to adjust to the changing conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Some people say left-handers have an advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:03.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,because right-handers aren't playing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,on their side of the lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,At most bowling alleys,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:09.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,they use a pattern of oil that is thicker in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,and thinner out toward the edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a forgiving layout
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:19.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,because balls that drift too far out start to hook earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:19.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:22.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,while balls going straighter can continue down the lane for longer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:22.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:25.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,before making their turn into the pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:25.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,But for pro bowlers, the oil conditions vary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:28.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,and players have to adjust their games to the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Some people seem to think that like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,league bowlers are better than they are, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,'cause they say like, "Oh, this league bowler
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,can shoot two 10, and I just saw pro shoot two 10."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's why they call it league
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,because you bowl on the same shot every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because each week on tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm bowling on a different condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not the same condition every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:51.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have Cheetah, Chameleon, Scorpion, shark,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:51.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,one more. - Bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:52.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Bear. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:53.90,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] But it's not just the oil on the lanes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是改变保龄球运动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,that is transformed bowling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是球道上的油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's also the balls themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,还有球本身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hard rubber bowling balls was what I started with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:03.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,我从硬质橡胶球开始打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe mid 70's and then the Yellow Dot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:08.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,the Columbia Yellow Dot, which is a plastic ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:08.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,大约70年代中期换成了“哥伦比亚黄点”  这是种塑料球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then they came out with urethane bowling balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:11.14,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后聚氨酯球出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I won a lot of titles with the urethane stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,我用这种球拿到了不少冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then they come out with the reactive resin bowling balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,再之后出现的是活性树脂材质的球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:20.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Reactive resin is just a modified polyurethane
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:20.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,这就是一种改良的聚氨酯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:23.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,with a more porous surface, which gives it more grip in the oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:23.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,它的表面疏松多孔  在涂油的地面上抓地性更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:28.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the most popular surface or cover stock for bowling balls today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:28.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是当下最流行的保龄球表面涂层
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Balls started out as perfect symmetrically-weighted spheres.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球最初是重量完美对称分布的球体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:36.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,And when you go to a bowling alley, the house balls there are still just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:36.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果你去保龄球馆看看  那里的公用球仍然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:38.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,But when you drill holes in the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:38.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是如果你在球上钻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,you take some weight out of one side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,就会让球在某个方向上的重量减少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,So to rebalance it, ball manufacturers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球的制造商为了重新调整球的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:46.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,added a small pancake weight on the same side as the holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:46.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,会在打孔的方向上加个配重饼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,But then ball manufacturers got the idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是制造商想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:52.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,they could add different weights inside the ball to improve their performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:52.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们可以在球的内部放置不同的配重  来提升球的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can have two balls that look identical from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,weigh exactly the same amount,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:57.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,外观相同、重量相等的两颗保龄球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,and yet roll differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,转起来可以完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:03.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,If the mass is more concentrated around the axis of rotation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:03.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果质量在旋转轴周围更加集中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:06.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,say you have a dense cylinder inside the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:06.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,比如在球内嵌了一个致密的圆柱体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well then it has a lower moment of inertia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,这颗球的转动惯量会较小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,And this means for the same amount of energy input,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,这意味着  对于相同大小的能量输入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,it will spin faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,它会旋转得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:16.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,In bowling, they prefer to talk about an analogous concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:16.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,在保龄球术语中有个相似的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Radius of gyration or RG.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,回转半径 缩写为RG
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you were to concentrate the entire mass of the ball
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果把整个球的质量集中在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,onto a hoop with the same moment of inertia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,一个有相同转动惯量的圆环上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's radius would be the radius of gyration.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个圆环的半径就是回转半径
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:32.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,So smaller radius of gyration just means lower moment of inertia,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:32.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以回转半径小就意味着转动惯量小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:36.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,which translates into more rotation that a bowler can get on the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:36.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,也就能使保龄球手将球转得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Some people are lower leverage
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,it just spins faster, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:40.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,eh, it's of crazy, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:42.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,somebody finally did a study on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:49.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,yeah, it's like 8% for every 0.05.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:49.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,And so it depends on what your leverage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can be fairly significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] An ability to spin the balls faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,只要能让球转的更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:18:00.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,gives a bowler the ability to hook the ball more sharply further down the lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:18:00.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球手就越可能在球道更远处  让球拐得更大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,giving them a better chance of achieving that six degree entry angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,也就越可能达到6°的入射角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,What was amazing for me to learn is that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,配重块的知识使我大受震撼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,the weight blocks in these balls aren't even centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:09.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,球里面的配重块甚至不位于中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a heavy side and a lighter side on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:12.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,制作商有意将它们制成一侧重一侧轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you can find and mark this side
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,by letting the ball spin freely on a cushion of air,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:17.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,让球在气垫上自由旋转  就可以找到哪边重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:20.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,until it comes to rest, heavy side down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:20.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,直到它静止下来 此时重的一侧向下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,They showed me a great demonstration
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们向我绝妙地展示了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,of how the position of the center of gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:26.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,can affect the movement of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:26.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,重心的位置对球的运动能产生怎样的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,When the center of mass is on the left side of the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,当质心位于球的左侧时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,it pulls in the same direction as the spin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,它的拉力和旋转摩擦力同向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,helping the ball hook to the left, into the pins,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,帮助球往左侧拐弯 击倒球瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Same exact ball, same numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,同一个球 同一个码数
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:41.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,just different static and balance basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:41.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,基本上只有平衡位置不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] But here is a flipped bowling ball
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,而这是个镜像翻转的保龄球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,where the center of mass is on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,,它的质心位于右侧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now the ball starts to hook into the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:49.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,现在球开始钩向左侧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:52.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,but at the end, something weird happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:52.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是最后奇怪的事情发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,The center of mass pulls it over to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,质心把球拉向右侧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:59.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,This effect is only really noticeable when the ball is thrown slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:59.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个效应只在缓慢投球的时候比较明显
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,These days, there are tons of different weight blocks that go inside bowling balls
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,现在的保龄球里  有各种各样的配重块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:10.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,and they can be grouped into two categories, symmetric and asymmetric.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:10.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,它们可以分为两类：对称的块和不对称的块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,For all these weight blocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,不管是哪类配重块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,the minimum moment of inertia or in bowling terms, the smallest RG axis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,转动惯量最小的轴  或者用保龄球术语来说“RG最小”的轴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:20.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,is identified by a pin, which is visible on the outside of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:20.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,都会在球的表面有所标记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,It will spin most easily about this axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:23.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球绕此轴旋转最不费力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,For the symmetric weight blocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,对于对称的配重块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,the ball doesn't change as you rotate it about this axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,球绕对称轴转动时  质量分布不变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the maximum moment of inertia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以要获得最大转动惯量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:36.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,is rotating about any axis that passes through the equator of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:36.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,只需让转动轴穿过赤道（即转动轴垂直于左图的对称轴）即可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,I certainly didn't expect bowling balls to have asymmetric cores,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,我当然没有料到保龄球会有不对称的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it turns out what looked like perfect spheres,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是看起来像是完美球体的保龄球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:46.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,actually have three different principal axes of rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:46.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,其实有三个不同的转动主轴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Minimum moment of inertia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:47.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,最小惯量轴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,maximum moment of inertia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,最大惯量轴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,and intermediate moment of inertia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,以及中间轴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So this right here is our Dark Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们这球叫“暗黑代码”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is one of our asymmetric ball that has the Rad 4 core in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:56.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是个非对称核心的球  里面放了“Rad 4”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,So this has a preferred spin axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以它有一个偏好的转轴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:19:59.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,And what we're going to do now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,is we're going to put it onto the determinator
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们现在要把球放在仪器上观察球的转动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,and show how it actually will spin it and find it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,no matter how we position it on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:05.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,无论我们以哪个方向把球放进仪器  它都能让球旋转、并找到转轴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] So you spin them up on this machine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:08.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以你先让球在机器上转起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,until they settle into the way they like to spin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:15.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,where the bowlers call their preferred spin axis or PSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:15.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,它们最后会绕着保龄球手所说的偏好转轴（PSA）转动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:19.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)\an8}（即 最大惯量轴）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:19.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,But why would you want a ball to be an asymmetric top?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:19.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是保龄球手为什么会希望球有一头不对称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, professional bowlers drill their balls
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,职业球手会在他们的球上钻孔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,so that at lunch the axis of rotation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,is somewhere between the minimum and maximum moment of inertia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:28.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以把球掷出时  旋转轴将位于最小惯量轴和最大惯量轴之间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,And as a result, as the ball goes down the lane spinning,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,这就导致了  当球沿着球道前进时会高速旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,it precesses like a gyroscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,像陀螺仪一样“进动”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,{\an7}进动：最常见于天文学\N指自转轴受某些因素影响\N相对于空间中的惯性坐标系\N所发生的缓慢且连续的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,The axis of rotation rotates around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,旋转轴在起始点周围旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,causing the point of contact between the ball and the lane to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,使得球与地面的接触点不断改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,This precession means that different parts of the ball contact the lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,这种进动意味着  球每自转一圈  接触地面的部分都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,{\an7}进动：最常见于天文学\N指自转轴受某些因素影响\N相对于空间中的惯性坐标系\N所发生的缓慢且连续的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:50.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,And you can see this when the ball back by the spread-out lines of oil on the ball surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:50.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,你可以观察到球面上一圈圈的油迹线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bowlers call this track flare, and it's desirable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,球手们称之为“瓜皮线”  这样的轨迹是比较理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:57.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,{\an7}*没查到track flare这个术语的中文\N翻译时只好直接根据\N视频中的形态来意译
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:57.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,because it means once the ball hits the unoiled part of the lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:57.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,这种轨迹意味着  球一旦进入到球道后程不涂油的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,it gets traction faster
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,它会更快地获得摩擦力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,and hooks more dramatically back to the pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,并且更显著地钩向球瓶的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is what asymmetric cores are used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:04.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,这就是非对称核心的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:08.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,They have larger differences between their moments of inertia in different axes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,or what bowlers call RG differential,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:10.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,其不同主轴上的转动惯量之差（术语“RG差值”）要更大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,which makes the ball precess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,这导致球会产生进动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you spin a ball around it's minimum or maximum moment of inertia,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果让球绕着最小/最大惯量轴旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:19.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,it processes less and there's much less flair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:19.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,进动的幅度会比较小  瓜皮线也会窄得多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:23.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,meaning oil builds up on one part of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:23.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,这意味着油会在球上的同一个部分积累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,This reduces the friction over the dry part of the lane
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,这会减少球在干燥地面上的摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,so the ball hooks less.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以钩球幅度会变小
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,- See the oil there, very faintly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,- 看这里的油迹 非常淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it's pretty much next to the finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,right next to the thumb,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:34.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,但在拇指周围相当多油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it just continues to be right that way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,痕迹沿着这条线延续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,all the way around the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,绕球一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:43.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] But how important are each of these factors in actually getting the best shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:43.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,但要想完美地一球全倒  这些因素到底有多少影响？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, the US Bowling Congress, or USBC,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,美国保龄球协会（USBC）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:50.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,the governing body that sets all rules and regulations for US bowling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:50.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,也就是设计了美国保龄球一切规则规章的管辖实体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:52.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,They did a landmark study in 2008,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:52.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们在2008年进行了一次重要的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:57.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,trying to tease out the most significant factors that affect ball motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:57.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,试图找出对保龄球的运动影响最大的因素
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,In order to determine the impact of each factor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,为了确定每个因素分别有多大影响
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,they had to make sure that throws were identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:02.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们需要确保每次投出的球都完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,So they turned to Harry,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:04.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以他们选择了“哈里”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:07.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,at the time, the most consistent bowler in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:07.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,当时他是世界上最稳定的保龄球手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,He is a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,“他”是个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:14.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bowling robots are designed to be able to throw hundreds of identical shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:14.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球机器人可以投出上千个完全一样的球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:18.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,In fact, the robot Earl, Harry's successor in 2011,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:18.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,实际上，哈里的传人——机器人“伯爵”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,actually lost to Chris Barnes when he debuted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,在它的出道战中输给了克里斯·巴恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:23.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,in part because his throws were so consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:23.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,部分原因是“伯爵”投的球太稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:27.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,He wore away the oil in a single part of the lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.97,0:22:27.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,它的球蹭掉了同一个路径上的油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,So his shots hooked too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以它的球拐弯的幅度太大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:34.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,The people managing him did their best to adjust to the oil conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.96,0:22:34.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,尽管“伯爵”的维护者尽了最大的努力来适应油的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:37.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,but few people are Chris Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:37.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,但他们毕竟比不了克里斯·巴恩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:39.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,The USBC ball motion study
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:42.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,used Harry to throw thousands of shots with different bowling balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:42.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,USBC的保龄球运动研究  使用了哈里来扔出数千个不同的球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:46.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,And they found that the center of gravity affected the ball motion relatively little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:46.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们发现  球的重心几乎不影响球的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:52.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Around the same level as environmental factors like room temperature or humidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:52.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,球的重心造成的影响力跟温度、湿度等环境因素半斤八两
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:54.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,RG, and RG differential,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:54.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,RG 和 RG 差值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:55.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,essentially the moment of inertia
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:55.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,也就是转动惯量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:59.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,and difference between maximum and minimum moments of inertia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:59.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,以及最大惯量与最小惯量的差值
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:02.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,That affected the ball motion significantly more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:02.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,转动惯量对球的运动的影响力明显更大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:07.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the factor that affected ball motion the most was the surface of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:07.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,但影响力最大的因素  是球的表面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,The top five individual factors were
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:10.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,影响最大的五个因素分别是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:12.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,the amplitude of surface roughness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:12.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,球面的粗糙度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,meaning the height of microscopic spikes on the ball;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:15.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,也就是球面上微小的突起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:18.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,the coefficient of friction with an oiled lane;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:18.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,球与球道打油部分之间的摩擦系数
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,the surface roughness by spacing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,球面粗糙处的空间分布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,that is the distance between microscopic spikes;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,即微小突起之间的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:26.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,the coefficient of friction with the dry lane;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:26.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,球与球道未打油部分之间的摩擦系数
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:29.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,and how quickly the ball surface absorbs oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:29.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,还有球吸收润滑油的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:33.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, bowlers recognize just how important the surface of their ball is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:33.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球手明白  自己的球的表面有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:37.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,They pay close attention to what it's made of and how it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:37.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们很重视球面的材料与抛光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:39.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Rougher finishes, give the ball more traction in the oil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:39.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,抛光时做粗糙  能让球在有油的部分获得更大牵引
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:42.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,and get it to start hooking earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:42.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,让保龄球能更快转向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:46.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is useful for long oil patterns and slower axis rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:46.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,这最适合打油部分较长的球道、自转较慢的球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:52.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sometimes maybe I'll go to a little more sanded ball or a little more ball surface
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:52.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,我有时会选择稍微粗糙一点的球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:54.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,to get it into a roll quicker for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.53,0:23:54.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,来让球转得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:56.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,because they use a lot of oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:56.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为能吸收更多润滑油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:58.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,- These two shots are thrown identically.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:58.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,这两个球以完全相同的姿态抛出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:02.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,The only difference is the ball on the left has a rougher surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.84,0:24:02.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,唯一的区别是，左边的球  表面更粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Rough surfaces act like winter tires,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:08.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,粗糙的表面就像冬季胎一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:12.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,helping to dig into the oil and give the ball traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:12.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,让球能更好地吸油、抓地、获得牵引力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:17.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,They also act as badly as winter tires on a clean road on a totally dry lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:17.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,冬季胎在干净路面上不好用  粗糙的球在没打油的球道上也亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:20.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,They actually have less friction because their rougher exteriors
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:23.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,mean that less surface area is touching the lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.44,0:24:23.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,此时它们的摩擦力反而更少  因为粗糙的表面导致抓地面积更少
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:26.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can get many different levels of smoothness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:26.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,光滑程度有几个不同的等级
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:29.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,up to a near mirror shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:29.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,最光滑的就像镜子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:31.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is better for short oil patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:31.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,这适合打油部分较短的球道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.41,0:24:34.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,to prevent the ball hooking too much, too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.41,0:24:34.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,这可以让球不会太早转向
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:38.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, pro bowlers carry many different balls to each competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:38.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,总的来说  保龄球的职业球手会带很多不同的球去比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:40.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'm not afraid to change balls in the middle of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:40.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,我不怕打到一半换球
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.66,0:24:45.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,I go to the game and I've got like a spare, a spare, a spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.66,0:24:45.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,比如说哪场比赛时我连续三次都是补中、补中、补中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.66,0:24:45.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,{\an7}spare：补中，在一轮比赛中\N第一球没有让球瓶全倒\N第二球才清掉了其余球瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:47.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right. It's time to change balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:47.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,行吧  应该换个球了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:47.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:47.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.89,0:24:49.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- So now I gotta find the right ball to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.89,0:24:49.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以我得找到最适合这个球道的球
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:52.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,get down the lane again and find the proper,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:52.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,把换了的球丢上球道  找到最适合这条道的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:54.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,which usually I have a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:54.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,很多时候我都知道该选哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.35,0:24:58.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,- [Derek] So they select their ball a little like a golfer selects their club,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.12,0:24:59.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,to suit the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.35,0:24:59.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以他们像高尔夫球手挑球杆一样  会根据赛道条件来选球
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:04.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,But does all this tech actually make people better bowlers?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:04.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,但这些技巧能让人打的更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.10,0:25:05.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, over the last 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.68,0:25:09.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,average scores have increased by more than five points.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.10,0:25:09.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,在过去二十年里，平均分数上升了超过五分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.01,0:25:13.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Plus the number of perfect 300 games bowled per year per thousand bowlers
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.01,0:25:13.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,每年每千人打出完美300分局的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:16.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,has increased dramatically since the 1980s.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.30,0:25:16.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,从上世纪80年代起  也有了不可思议的增长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.56,0:25:20.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,This graph shows the percent change year over year.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.56,0:25:20.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个表展示了每年完美局的占比
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.41,0:25:21.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,In 1976,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.41,0:25:21.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,在1976年
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.65,0:25:26.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,soaker balls, balls chemically softened to absorb oil and hook more, were banned,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.65,0:25:26.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,海绵球被禁止了  这种球是用化学手段软化的  更加吸油、转向更好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.64,0:25:29.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there was a dip in perfect games.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.64,0:25:29.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,完美局的比例大幅下跌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:31.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,But the same year a new rubber ball was introduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:33.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,the Brunswick LT-48
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.29,0:25:33.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,但同年，一种新型的橡胶球“不伦瑞克 LT-48”发售了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.86,0:25:37.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,and more 300 were hit in the years that followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.86,0:25:37.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,完美局的比例在下一年又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.33,0:25:40.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,In 1991, reactive resin balls were introduced
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.33,0:25:40.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,在1991年，树脂球发布
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.20,0:25:42.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,and there was another significant jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.20,0:25:42.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,这个比例又一次增长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.66,0:25:47.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, obviously there were other improvements in equipment and natural variability,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.66,0:25:47.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,很明显  现在的设备更加完善  环境变量也更加稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.34,0:25:49.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,but some of the big changes do correlate
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.53,0:25:52.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,with the introduction of new ball technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.34,0:25:52.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,但最大的影响还来自于新型球的发布
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.35,0:25:55.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,So yes, the wild bowling ball technologies out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.35,0:25:55.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以  每当一种疯狂的保龄球黑科技出现时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.37,0:25:57.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,especially anything to do with surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.37,0:25:57.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,尤其是跟球面有关的科技
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.58,0:26:01.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,significantly affect ball motion and your bowling game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.58,0:26:01.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,都会显著地影响球的运动、影响比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.84,0:26:05.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,But ball motion is likely minutely affected by hundreds of other factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.84,0:26:05.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,不过还有数百个因素对球的运动产生微小的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.77,0:26:08.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Even the color of the ball can have a small impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.77,0:26:08.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,甚至球的颜色也会产生微小的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.51,0:26:11.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,A USBC study in 2016 found that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.51,0:26:11.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,USBC在2016年的一次研究发现
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:15.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,different pigments absorb oil at different rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.41,0:26:15.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,不同的涂料吸收润滑油的速度不同
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.43,0:26:18.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bowling is the sport of re-invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.43,0:26:18.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球是再发明的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.05,0:26:19.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,That goes back to ancient Egypt,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.05,0:26:19.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,其历史能够追溯到古埃及
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.74,0:26:22.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,but has transformed many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.74,0:26:22.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,但已经多次脱胎换骨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.38,0:26:24.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, when you get up to throw a single shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.38,0:26:24.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,现在，当你要扔出一个球时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:27.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,you have to think about the oil pattern on the lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.46,0:26:27.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,你要考虑球道上润滑油的厚度
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:30.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,the stage of the game and how the pattern has shifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:30.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,比赛的阶段、润滑油厚度的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.16,0:26:31.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,the weight block in your ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.16,0:26:31.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,保龄球里的配重块
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.59,0:26:33.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,whether you want symmetric or asymmetric,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.59,0:26:33.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,是对称还是非对称
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.81,0:26:37.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,which axis you'll spin it about to affect precession,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.81,0:26:37.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,让它以哪个轴旋转  来影响进动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:39.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,where the center of mass is to pull the ball to the left, to the right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:39.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,球的质心会把球往左拉还是往右拉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.80,0:26:41.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,what the cover stock is made of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.80,0:26:41.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,球面是什么材质
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:43.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,and whether it's rough or smooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:43.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,是粗糙还是光滑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.67,0:26:47.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,all to make a shot that skids, hooks, and rolls
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.67,0:26:47.08,CHN,,0,0,0,,只为了能够扔出一球  经过滑行、转弯、滚动
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.08,0:26:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,to the pins between boards 17 and 18 and a half
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.08,0:26:50.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.24,0:26:53.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,at as close to a six degree angle as you can master.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.24,0:26:53.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,尽量以6°的入射角  打到17号+半条18号板上的球瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:57.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now do that again 12 times in a row
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:57.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,丢出12次完美球
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.96,0:27:00.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you have a perfect game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.96,0:27:00.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,你就达成了完美局
